Version 1.0.5 - June 11, 2007
   - Fixed links to "new comments" in sidebar.
   - Fixed mangling of text type when posting responses.

Version 1.0.4 - Sep 21, 2005
   - Support for atom autodiscovery.
   - Support for robot exclusion headers.
   - Explicitly put focus on popup login windows and, if possible, center
     them over the parent window.

Version 1.0.3 - Jun  24, 2005
   - Support for anonymous posting of comments.

Version 1.0.2 - May 5, 2005
   - Fix bug where all comments have item author's name on them.
   - Fix crash due to "newcomments" typo in sidebar.
   - Use conference title instead of bbsname in most title lines.
   - Add RSS autodiscovery links and RSS button display.
   - Slight increase in pop-up login box size.

Version 1.0.1 - Nov 10, 2004
   - Add peekconf.bt and peekresp.bt scripts so this can be used with peek
     interface.
   - rename macros.bt to links.bt to conform with rss interface conventions.

Version 1.0.0 - Jul 12, 2004
   - Original release.
